HOW TO USE"Period Pain Relief Patches•Take out the strip from cover.•Peel off the protective liner from the cuts in the middle•Place it uniformly over the pain affected area – lower Back or lower abdomen (below the belly).•Dispose in the bin after use.Disposal Bags• Take out I LOVE CLEAN Bag from the box.•Insert the product to be disposed off from the open end of the bag.•Take off/remove plastic under the flap(for the adhesive to work)•Press & paste the flap properly(to protect it from opening.)•Dispose off(PLEASE DON'T FLUSH,THROW in a BIN.)Intimate Wet Wipes• Peel Front label slowly. • Pull out wipes as needed.•Re-seal label after each use to prevent moisture loss.PeeBuddy•Gently press the top front & back to POP open the pee-buddy•Move your panties aside,place the open end of the funnel/Pee-Buddy between your Legs right under the flow area.•Tilt Hips/Bend a little, ensure the funnel is tilted downwards, Relax & pee.•Dispose off in the bin."

Title: cosderma ZGTS dermaroller 2mm Vitamin C Hyaluronic Acid Serum(Set of 2)
Description: Alone Dermaroller never gives desired results you need to use good serum so that serum gets penetrated in deeper layers of skin when you make puncturing to skin with dermaroller & gives awesome results in just few sittings The ZGTS 2 mm titanium derma roller is one of the strongest derma rollers available on the market. It's needles are made from a titanium alloy so they are made to last. This derma roller is most suitable for use on less sensitive and delicate areas. It is ideal for stretch mark removal and scar reduction treatments on fleshy areas on the body (like tummy, thighs, etc). The titanium built needles will ensure many months of skin needling pleasure. It is popular with those people looking to use a derma roller for skin problems such as stretch marks and scars. It is suitable for use on all types of skin and is considered a very effective roller. HYALURONIC ACID SERUM bind with moisture on the skin to fill up fine lines, minimising the appearance of wrinkles. The wrinkle reducer helps skin feel and look smoother while protecting skin with Vitamin C it has great skin whitening result, HA + Vitamin C Serum Cosderma Vitamin C 10% with Hyaluronic Acid Serum Helps reduce appearance of fine lines • Intense hydration, Fights Against Signs of Aging • Brightens complexion, This serum is ideal for all skin types. Vitamin C Serum is the perfect solution for your anti-aging and wrinkle needs. Premium ingredients deliver potent results by nourishing and strengthening the skin, helping to diminish the appearance of fine lines, wrinkles, age spots, sun spots, and other skin pigmentationHow to use the ZGTS titanium roller with Cosderma MesoserumHow to use 1)Clean Face with normal water or spirit & Dry 2) Apply Cosderma Vit c+ Hyaluronic Acid Serum All over Face 3) The roller is moved across the area of skin to be treated in a series of sequential movements. 2) Press firmly but do not overdo this to avoid any unnecessary discomfort. 3) One way of using a roller is to imitate the points of a compass and roll it front, left, right and then backwards. This ensures even coverage without overdoing it. 4) Re- Apply coat of serum if required 5) Your skin will feel warm and tight after use and will have a reddish color similar to a case of mild sunburn. This is entirely normal and will ease within 24 hours. 6) Clean If any redness or bleeding & finally apply 1 more coating of serum all over face & wash face after 3 hours Amazing Results you will get to see in just 1-3 with such procedure, you can repeat session after 10-15 days for best results

Title: Sirona Travel Hygiene Kit for Her(Set of 6)
Description: Travel on your mind? Take or Gift SIRONA's Travel Hygiene Kit for her. A specially designed kit, this takes care of Travel Woes unique to Women. The kit contains, PeeBuddy – Pack of 5 - (Using which women can Stand & Pee in all dirty/common toilets - its portable, disposable, easy to carry and ideal for Rail/Air Travel/Fuel stations/Treks/Camps - - No more wiping of seat or making chairs), Disposal Bags (10 Bags For Discreet, Tamper Proof & Hygienic Disposal of Sanitary Products including Pads/Tampons/Panty Liners), Multi Use Wet Wipes (10 Wipes), Intimate Wet Wipes (10 Wipes with Aloe Vera/Fruit Extracts) for her body (Bikini Area, Under Arm, Breast), Natural Mosquito Patches ( 24 patches for Protection from mosquitoes/Deet Free), & India’s First Herbal Period Pain Relief Patches (Herbal/Long Lasting/Discreet/No more Pills/Sprays, now sleep & Travel well) which can take care of pains during Periods (can be used on stomach/Back/legs) – 5 Patches. HOW TO USE"PeeBuddy•Gently press the top front & back to POP open the pee-buddy•Move your panties aside,place the open end of the funnel/Pee-Buddy between your Legs right under the flow area.•Tilt Hips/Bend a little, ensure the funnel is tilted downwards, Relax & pee.•Dispose off in the bin.Disposal Bags• Take out I LOVE CLEAN Bag from the box.•Insert the product to be disposed off from the open end of the bag.•Take off/remove plastic under the flap(for the adhesive to work)•Press & paste the flap properly(to protect it from opening.)•Dispose off(PLEASE DON'T FLUSH,THROW in a BIN.)Multi Use Wet Wipes• Peel Front label slowly. • Pull out wipes as needed.•Re-seal label after each use to prevent moisture loss.Intimate Wet Wipes• Peel Front label slowly. • Pull out wipes as needed.•Re-seal label after each use to prevent moisture loss.Natural Mosquito Patches•Each strip contains 2 patches•Pull out the patch from strip•Peel off the protective film•Stick the patch on clothes•Dispose off after usePeriod Pain Relief Patches•Take out the strip from cover.•Peel off the protective liner from the cuts in the middle•Place it uniformly over the pain affected area – lower Back or lower abdomen (below the belly).•Dispose in the bin after use."

Remove the cap on the Developer. Remove the cap on the Developer. Remove the cap on the colorant.Carefully pour the required amount of the Colorant & Developer into Foaming Pump bottle.Delicately rotate the bottle to gently mix the color. Do not shake.Push the pump of the Foaming bottle. Dispense suitable foam on the palm of your gloved hand. Do not apply directly to hair.Spread throughout the hair starting at the top of your head. Leave in for 10 minutes.Rinse it with warm water until water runs clear. Saturate your hair with the enclosed treatment & leave on for 2 - 3 minutes before rinsing thoroughly with warm water.
